Subject: [PATCH 1/5] chore: update configuration and improve error handling

- Added .env to .dockerignore to prevent sensitive data exposure.
- Refactored blog metadata injection to use configuration from site.config.json.
- Enhanced BlogService to handle errors when loading posts and set error state.
- Updated navigation service to use signals for sidebar and mobile navigation items.
- Improved SEO service to utilize environment variables for site name and URL.
- Added aria attributes and error messages in contact form for better accessibility.
- Updated various components to ensure proper data binding and error handling.
